resources.string: Engeza iqoqo lakho lomuntu ku-Beta yomculo uphinde ufinyelele kulo ngokushesha kusukela kunoma iyiphi ikhompyutha exhunyiwe noma idivayisi ye-Android.
Xhuma idivayisi yakho kukhomputha ngentambo ye-USB ukuze ukopishe umculo kudivayisi yakho. Uma une-Macintosh, layisha uhlelo lokudlulisa lefayela le-Android kuqala kukhompyutha yakho.
